definition.text: Now that everything's clear, let's do the switch and get ready for what comes next!

paragraphs.text: This is what you need to do:
Go back to the footer and select Develop as your Current Branch.
You will get a page explaining what is being done. Once the process finishes, you will get another page telling you of the outcome.
Stop / close the app (browser and console).
Find the Contribute to Superalgos Tutorial in the bottom-right corner of the workspace and select Resume in the menu!
